==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yòu hăo xìao, yòu hăo qì

===Idiom===
'''[[又]][[好]][[笑]]，[[又]][[好]][[气]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# Not know whether to laugh or get angry.

===Alternate forms===
[[又]][[好]][[笑]]，[[又]][[好]][[氣]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])


